{{if eq .agent "claude-code"}}Interview me using the AskUserQuestionTool relentlessly about every aspect of this plan until we reach a shared understanding.{{else}}Ask the user directly in conversation relentlessly about every aspect of this plan until reaching a shared understanding.{{end}} For each question, include your weighted recommendation [strong|neutral|weak]. Walk down each branch of the design tree, resolving dependencies between decisions one-by-one.

If a question can be answered by exploring the codebase, explore the codebase instead.

If a relevant PRD already exists in `{{.plans_dir}}`, read it first for context.
{{if .report_bugs}}
## Bug reports

If any plan-bender command (`pb` or `pba`) fails or behaves unexpectedly, write a detailed bug report to `pb-error-report-<UTC-timestamp>.log` in the project root (e.g. `pb-error-report-20260502T143000Z.log`). Include the exact command, full stdout/stderr, expected vs actual behavior, the relevant `.plan-bender.yaml` config, the issue/PRD slug in play, and `pb --version`. Tell the user where you saved it and link to https://github.com/jasonraimondi/plan-bender/issues so they can file it.
{{end}}
